<P>A tear fell from Don I&s;idor, and the Baron re&s;umed his &s;tory.</P>
<P>At this period Peter called forth all his <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">, to cru&s;h a confederacy formed again&s;t him <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;ome di&s;contented nobles, at the head of which were his mother and his half brother. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">
