<P>Rely, ladies, &s;aid Alphon&s;o, upon &s;uch protec|tion as I and my &s;ervant can afford you; and re&s;t a&s;&s;ured that we will &s;till defend you while we have life to move an arm.</P>
<P>It is not a few Portugue&s;e that &s;hall hurt you, &s;aid Pierrot, with a bow to the chai&s;e, by way of hint to the ladies to be of good che<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">k.</P>
