<P>Alphon&s;o was in an agony of de&s;pair&mdash;he im|mediately took hor&s;e and pur&s;ued them in the route towards the confines of Spain, till their hor&s;es were unable to proceed, and he found pur&s;uit vain. Alas! &s;aid he, what a wretch am I, to have &s;een &s;uch beauty, and to have it &s;natched from me in an in&s;tant!&mdash;Ungrateful <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> mark, no proof of gratitude or regard!&mdash;Oh God! Oh God! would that I were dead!</P>
