<P>Ble&s;&s;ed be your heart, my hone&s;t Pierrot! re|turned Alphon&s;o; never &s;hall this be forgotten to thee: for this, even this, will be &s;ome com|fort, &s;ome <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span">, under my mi&s;eries.</P>
