<P>There again, returned the youth, you <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> the madne&s;s occa&s;ioned by your fears. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;ot, do you not perceive that it is yet <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> morning? Even now the &s;un barely <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">
