<P>That is impo&s;&s;ible, &s;aid Don I&s;idor; bu&s;ine&s;s of con&s;equence obliges us to return with ha&s;te&punc; we wi&s;h the worthy Marquis all the felicity &s;uch virtues merit, and will offer up our prayers to the Virgin to ble&s;s his nuptials. However, I thank you for the pains you have taken to inform me, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> reque&s;t that you will accept this&mdash;giving <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> a piece of money&mdash;and make mercy with <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> another occa&s;ion. Then turning their <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> they proceeded on their journey.</P>
