<P>Then let him die&mdash;a &s;on of the hou&s;e of Rayo knows how to die, but cannot know di&s;honour&mdash;nor can Heaven receive a more delightful &s;a|crifice than that of a virtuous &s;on immolated at the &s;hrine of his parent's honour.</P>
