<P>The lady then threw her&s;elf down upon the couch, wept bitterly, and remained immoveable&mdash;The prie&s;t then withdrew and brought away the others, &s;aying, it was probable that nature exhau&s;ted was &s;inking into &s;leep.</P>
<P>And who may the&s;e people be? &s;aid the officer.&mdash;Hu&s;h, &s;aid the prie&s;t, let us begone!&mdash;They returned into the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">ult, and &s;hut the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> them&mdash;Be particular, &s;aid the prie&s;t to the officer, in noting the conver&s;ation you have ju&s;t heard.</P>
