<P>You have now, &s;aid he to Fernando, brought trea&s;on to my doors, and 'tis fit that you &s;hould die: to make vengeance more complete; I will wait till your mother revives to behold it. Al|phon&s;o could no longer re&s;train him&s;elf, but ru&s;h|ing again&s;t the door &s;plintered it to pieces&mdash;Villain! cried he, hold your murderous hand, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> this in&s;tant thou die&s;t!</P>
